 Mission_Intent_Blufor {
  coords 2374.469 163.5 1873.96
  m_sTitle "VI. Mission Intent (Mission Maker)"
  m_sTextData "Mission intent is to loosely replicate the battles that took place in the Korengal Valley. "\
  ""\
  "Mission intent is not for Blufor to fight from the hills, villages, across the AO."\
  ""\
  "Blufor is permitted to leave the COP and patrol the area to scout. It is recommended not to commit too much manpower outside the COP. Blufor is also permitted to detach some of the platoon and have them take up fighting positions in OP Restrepo or Firebase Vegas."\
  ""\
  "You can teleport to the fighting positions, but you cannot teleport back. OP Restrepo has vehicles if falling back is needed. "\
  ""\
  "Blufor can use the MATVs to get around outside of the COP, however the terrain is extremely restrictive. If a vehicle rolls over due to basic physics and not an Arma-related issue, that is still in play and GMs should consider not rectifying it."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 6
 }
}